---
title: Easy Tex-Mex Crumbed Chicken & Celery Slaw with Sweetcorn Crushed Potatoes
description: You can jazz up anything with a bit of bling, like these crushed potatoes, simply add golden corn to the mix and they are ready to make mouths water. Another example, a crunchy crumb to Tex-Mex spiced chicken does wonders to make this dinner stand out from the crowd!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
